.claude/** whitespace=-trailing-space,-blank-at-eof
.codex/** whitespace=-trailing-space,-blank-at-eof
.planning/** whitespace=-trailing-space,-blank-at-eof
.specify/** whitespace=-trailing-space,-blank-at-eof

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
